cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CV 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it presents an extension of LSTM neural networks for language modeling and machine translation tasks. Additionally, the paper may also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as it proposes a new architecture for neural networks. The use of gating functions is a common technique in neural networks, which may also make this paper relevant to cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Finally, the paper may also be relevant to cs.CV (Computer Vision) as LSTMs have been used in image captioning tasks.
